    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document examines the general framework of Realm Specific IP (RSIP).  RSIP is intended as a alternative to NAT in which the end-to- end integrity of packets is maintained.  We focus on implementation issues, deployment scenarios, and interaction with other layer-three protocols.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
